snippet.title: WANTED RACCOON - announce trailer Early Access
snippet.description:
Add WANTED RACCOON to your Wishlist on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1320100/Wanted_Raccoon/

Download our Press Kit! https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/12InzR8Yc8SL9rz_5zsf9P5Q0MkHte9Xp?usp=sharing

Discord: https://discord.gg/RRGSj4Xb86
Website: https://wantedraccoon.com/
Email: raccoonwanted@gmail.com
___________________________________
WANTED RACCOON is a 3rd person raccoon simulator with a storyline and a vast space to explore. Steal food, skateboard, do dirty tricks, fight people, create equipment, upgrade your skills, find the kidnapped family and lead the resistance. 

Developer, Publisher: MAD sprouts

Genres: Action, Adventure, Stealth, Casual, Simulator, Role-playing game, Humor

Release: 19.03.2021 (Early Access)

Price: 19,99$

Platforms: Windows, Linux

Engine: Unity

Gameplay: The game is in the genre of sandbox, action, survival, where you are to play for a raccoon, organize the resistance of animals and confront people.
